channel.title: Looking for a coder!
channel.description:
[b]Hello Everyone, My name is Adiv.
I'm willing to invest VPS on RSPS server, My cousin is going to publish the server to a lot of runescape players. I would like server with donations that will help me in the future with the VPS money. I've thought that the server will be 718+ PVP@SPAWN. Long time ago I had a few success servers they was closed due money issues.
I'm really looking for a serious programmer, the programmer need to show me at least one of his work that he worked on. My skype is: Adivush26.[/b]
